---
import GridContainer from '../layouts/GridContainer.astro'
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
import Cal from '../components/Cal.astro'
import Header from '../layouts/Header.astro'
---

<Layout
	title="RPTrainor: Turn Your Influence into a Thriving Business with Custom Apps"
	description="Join RPTrainor in transforming your large audience into a thriving business. We build and maintain custom branded apps tailored to enhance your brand visibility. Start with just a $500 retainer and partner with us for lasting successâ€”paying only 30% equity."
>
	<Header />
	<GridContainer>
		<div
			class="short:col-span-3 short:col-start-1 short:px-4 col-span-3 col-start-1 row-start-2 px-4 pb-4 sm:col-span-1 sm:col-start-2 sm:px-0"
		>
			<h1
				class="short:text-xl tall:text-4xl max-w-2xl text-balance text-left text-2xl font-bold leading-tight tracking-tight text-white xs:text-3xl"
			>
				Transforming Creators into Entrepreneurs with Custom App Development
			</h1>
			<p
				class="extra-short:hidden short:text-base tall:text-xl short:mt-4 mt-4 block max-w-2xl text-balance text-left text-base leading-tight text-gray-300 xs:mt-8 xs:text-lg"
			>
				Leverage your large audience into a profitable venture with RPTrainor. We specialize in
				creating and managing custom branded apps to boost your brand visibility. Begin with a
				simple $500 retainer, and achieve greater success with only a 30% equity partnership.
				Discover how to elevate your brand today!
			</p>
		</div>

		<div
			class="short:col-span-3 short:col-start-1 short:px-4 col-span-3 col-start-1 row-start-3 px-4 sm:col-span-1 sm:col-start-2 sm:px-0"
		>
			<div class="flex items-center justify-between xs:gap-x-4 gap-x-2">
				<a
					onclick="Calendly.initPopupWidget({url: 'https://calendly.com/rptrainor/initial-strategy-session?hide_gdpr_banner=1&background_color=010203&text_color=ffffff&primary_color=d4af37'});return false;"
					aria-describedby="retainer"
					class="tall:text-lg rounded-xl bg-white px-3.5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-background shadow-sm hover:animate-hover-pop focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-contrast"
					>Reserve your slot</a
				>
				<a
					href="/process"
					class="tall:text-lg rounded-xl bg-none px-3.5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-white shadow-sm hover:animate-hover-pop hover:bg-white/20 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-contrast"
					>Talk with Ryan</a
				>
			</div>
		</div>
	</GridContainer>
	<GridContainer>
		<Cal />
	</GridContainer>
</Layout>
